title: Rank 2 OOL Team LF D3+ Jg
body: Team Reticent is looking for a jungler who shares a competitive mentality and a passion to reach OCS. If you have 5s experience and are willing to commit for the rest of the competitive split, hit me up in-game.

replies.body: Whatup my homie Turlo I am happy to play as an emergency sub if needed.
I'm a mid laner LFT... Add me in game - Cadence LFT
hey mate. Just some friendly advice but most teams are looking for current season ranked players not previous season titles. Best of luck :)
